-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);mask-composite:subtract;-webkit-clip-path:padding-box\"></span><span style=\"--speed:3s;--bg-size:300%;--color-from:#ffaa40;--color-to:#9c40ff;will-change:background-position;contain:content\" class=\"animate-gradient inline bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-from)] via-[var(--color-to)] to-[var(--color-from)] bg-[length:var(--bg-size)_100%] bg-clip-text text-transparent relative z-10 text-sm font-medium\">Hi，我是朱棣文✨</span></button></div><div class=\"flex\"><span class=\"inline-block text-muted-foreground max-w-[600px] md:text-lg lg:text-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(8px);transform:translateY(-8px)\">以理性为笔，以热爱为墨，写尽对世界的壮阔向往。</span></div></div><div class=\"order-1 md:order-2\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(6px);transform:translateY(-6px)\"><div class=\"relative size-24 md:size-32 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-[inset_0_-8px_10px_#8fdfff1f]\"><span class=\"animate-gradient absolute inset-0 block h-full w-full rounded-[inherit] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ffaa40]/50 via-[#9c40ff]/50 to-[#ffaa40]/50 bg-[length:300%_100%] p-[1px]\" style=\"-webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);-webkit-mask-composite:destination-out;mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);mask-composite:subtract;-webkit-clip-path:padding-box\"></span><img src=\"/me.png\" alt=\"文海星辰\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full\"/></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\"><div class=\"flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-y-4\"><div style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(6px);transform:translateY(-6px)\"><div class=\"relative px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer shadow-[inset_0_-8px_10px_#8fdfff1f] transition-shadow duration-500 ease-out hover:shadow-[inset_0_-5px_10px_#8fdfff3f] text-xl font-bold\" style=\"background:transparent;border:none;overflow:hidden\"><span class=\"animate-gradient absolute inset-0 block h-full w-full rounded-[inherit] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ffaa40]/50 via-[#9c40ff]/50 to-[#ffaa40]/50 bg-[length:300%_100%] p-[1px]\" style=\"-webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);-webkit-mask-composite:destination-out;mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);mask-composite:subtract;-webkit-clip-path:padding-box\"></span><span style=\"--speed:3s;--bg-size:300%;--color-from:#ffaa40;--color-to:#9c40ff;will-change:background-position;contain:content\" class=\"animate-gradient inline bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-from)] via-[var(--color-to)] to-[var(--color-from)] bg-[length:var(--bg-size)_100%] bg-clip-text text-transparent relative z-10 font-semibold\">平生自述🖊️</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(6px);transform:translateY(-6px)\"><div class=\"prose max-w-full text-pretty font-sans leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground dark:prose-invert\"><p>自2013年9月赴江城武汉，我便在此开启了漫长的创业求索之路。</p>\n<p>数载浮沉，尝过世事风霜，也遇过人间光亮，在起落之间沉淀心性，于得失之中认清方向。</p>\n<p>行至2019年末，我选择与过往作别，转身奔赴全新的人生旷野。\n从前在商海逐浪，如今以代码为舟，在理性与逻辑的世界里继续前行。\n半生辗转，初心未改，依旧相信热爱自有力量，前路皆有奔赴。</p>\n<p>闲暇时偏爱打篮球，在汗水与心跳里保持热忱与鲜活，以少年心气，对抗岁月漫长。</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"work\"><div class=\"flex min-h-0 flex-col gap-y-6\"><div style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(6px);transform:translateY(-6px)\"><div class=\"relative px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer shadow-[inset_0_-8px_10px_#8fdfff1f] transition-shadow duration-500 ease-out hover:shadow-[inset_0_-5px_10px_#8fdfff3f] text-xl font-bold\" style=\"background:transparent;border:none;overflow:hidden\"><span class=\"animate-gradient absolute inset-0 block h-full w-full rounded-[inherit] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ffaa40]/50 via-[#9c40ff]/50 to-[#ffaa40]/50 bg-[length:300%_100%] p-[1px]\" style=\"-webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);-webkit-mask-composite:destination-out;mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);mask-composite:subtract;-webkit-clip-path:padding-box\"></span><span style=\"--speed:3s;--bg-size:300%;--color-from:#ffaa40;--color-to:#9c40ff;will-change:background-position;contain:content\" class=\"animate-gradient inline bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-from)] via-[var(--color-to)] to-[var(--color-from)] bg-[length:var(--bg-size)_100%] bg-clip-text text-transparent relative z-10 font-semibold\">序章与征途⚓️</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(6px);transform:translateY(-6px)\"><div class=\"w-full grid gap-6\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"w-full border-b-0 grid gap-2\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_2dsdbtb_\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" id=\"radix-_R_dsdbtb_\" class=\"flex flex-1 items-center justify-between text-sm font-medium text-left [&amp;[data-state=open]_svg]:rotate-180 hover:no-underline p-0 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 ease-out rounded-xl group [&amp;&gt;svg]:hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground active:scale-[0.96] active:-translate-y-0.5 px-3 py-2 -mx-3\" data-radix-collection-item=\"\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-3 justify-between w-full text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-3 flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"size-8 md:size-10 rounded-full flex-none relative overflow-hidden shadow-[inset_0_-4px_6px_#8fdfff1f]\"><span class=\"animate-gradient absolute inset-0 block h-full w-full rounded-[inherit] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ffaa40]/50 via-[#9c40ff]/50 to-[#ffaa40]/50 bg-[length:300%_100%] p-[1px]\" style=\"-webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);-webkit-mask-composite:destination-out;mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);mask-composite:subtract;-webkit-clip-path:padding-box\"></span><img src=\"/atomic.png\" alt=\"独立技术创业者\" cla